INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(62, 1, '2011-09-21 20:52:38', '2011-09-21 20:52:38', '<div class="scrn-col-left">\r\n\r\n<h3>THE PRIVATE-PUBLIC SCREENINGS</h3>\r\n<p>The idea is simple – in february and march 2011, with the project AN ISLAND made with the band Efterklang, we experimented a new way to show the film – by letting people host their own screenings, where they wanted. The success was quite unexpected, and gave me the idea to continue to show my films in such a way.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From now on, you are welcome, through this page, to organize your own screening of ANY of my films, where you desire, when you want.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There is a few rules to follow:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The screenings need to have free entrance</li>\r\n<li>The screenings need to be public.</li>\r\n<li>The screenings need to have a minimum capacity of 5 people</li>\r\n<li>The screenings need to be verified by Vincent Moon and only screenings that are featured on <a href="petitesplanetes.cc">petitesplanetes.cc</a> are official screenings</li>\r\n<li>The screenings can take place in your home, at a café, in a school auditorium, in a bar, in the</li><li>streets… Any place, really.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>I hope you will enjoy seeing the films in such a way. You are welcome to pick any film i have made over the years, and not only the ones from Petites Planetes. You can even ask me for some unreleased ones – the complete list of films is on <a href="http://vincentmoon.com/">vincentmoon.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>HOW DOES IT WORK – TECHNICALLY SPEAKING?\r\n<p>I upload all my films on vimeo – <a href="http://vimeo.com/vincentmoon/videos">vimeo.com/vincentmoon/videos</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can download the films in good quality from there.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you would like to use a DVD player to screen the film then you can burn a playable DVD using a DVD burner application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can either connect it to a projector or one of those modern TVs, or simply screen it on your computer´s screen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My films very often contains MUSIC. So it will be better if you get a very good sound system – its often more important than the quality of the image.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>COPYRIGHT</h3>\r\n<p>Except where otherwise noted, all content relating to All my Work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-Share Alike 3.0 License. For more information please visit: <a href="http://www.creativecommons.org/about/licenses/">creativecommons.org/about/licenses/</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n', 'Host a Screening', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '40-revision-5', '', '', '2011-09-21 20:52:38', '2011-09-21 20:52:38', '', 40, 'http://cmky.us/esperando/40-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
